{"tid":2077544,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"仆街, 班ching蝦我地連登仔!","createTime":"2020-06-24T10:57:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-25T06:08:13.000Z","uid":61763,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"dbd4e04d852abf6e96b3b4a7e5919c09aed6e656","tid":2077544,"uid":61763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T10:57:29.000Z","msg":"屌喇星, 連登仔只有我先可以蝦!<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkepc.com/19490/10_%E7%9B%B8_50A___3950X_%E4%B9%9F_OK_ASROCK_B550M_Steel_Legend_%E4%B8%BB%E6%A9%9F%E6%9D%BF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkepc.com%2F19490%2F10_%25E7%259B%25B8_50A___3950X_%25E4%25B9%259F_OK_ASROCK_B550M_Steel_Legend_%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E6%25A9%259F%25E6%259D%25BF&d=Dkz3eIcuz1ZryPyeMF8ZPoE4T4y%2BYV5jPOnVoTo%2FPYs%3D&h=bdf09ac1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkepc.com/19490/10_%E7%9B%B8_50A___3950X_%E4%B9%9F_OK_ASROCK_B550M_Steel_Legend_%E4%B8%BB%E6%A9%9F%E6%9D%BF</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>採用 uPI-Semi UP9509S VRM 控制晶片</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://file1.hkepc.net/2020/06/source/2013503939652958740.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffile1.hkepc.net%2F2020%2F06%2Fsource%2F2013503939652958740.jpg&h=4f687488&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖就9505, 寫就9509, 真係ON99<br />\nUP9505S, 4+2<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.upi-semi.com/en-article-upi-362-2116\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.upi-semi.com%2Fen-article-upi-362-2116&d=Dkz3eIcuz1ZryPyeMF8ZPoE4T4y%2BYV5jPOnVoTo%2FPYs%3D&h=48d2f155\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.upi-semi.com/en-article-upi-362-2116</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>採用 uPI-Semi UP9509S VRM 控制晶片，CPU 供電部分透過 2 顆 uP1911R Doubler 晶片分拆訊號，控制兩組 4 顆 Vishay Siliconix SiC654 Dr.MOS 晶片</blockquote><br />\nUP1911R<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.upi-semi.com/en-article-upi-681-2163\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.upi-semi.com%2Fen-article-upi-681-2163&d=Dkz3eIcuz1ZryPyeMF8ZPoE4T4y%2BYV5jPOnVoTo%2FPYs%3D&h=d346bb6c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.upi-semi.com/en-article-upi-681-2163</a><br />\nUP1911R係雙DOUBLER=雙[1開2], 即係2開4, 唔係QUADRUPLER=1開4<br />\n<br />\nUP1911R可以從PWM IC食2條PWM而再射4條PWM出去<br />\nASROCK呢到點睇都似係UP9505S射4條PWM出去, 透過2粒UP1911R合共出8條PWM畀8粒SIC654 POWER STAGE去CPU<br />\n呢到係4倍8相, 不過唔係常見情況咁用4粒DOUBLER去達成, 而係只係用咗2粒雙DOUBLER去做<br />\n簡單D睇就好似兩粒DOUBLER痴埋一齊封裝成1粒CHIP咁, 即係類似DRMOS呢D將原本3粒野(上橋, 下橋, 驅動)封裝埋一齊做1粒CHIP<br />\n<br />\n如果真係QUADRUPLER的話例如IR3599咁係2倍8<br />\n1粒IR3599從PWM IC食1條PWM再屙返4條PWM出去,由食到屙當中係經同1個CONTROL LOGIC<br />\n相反雙DOUBLER UP1911R入面係有2個SEQUENCE CIRCUIT各食1條PWM去屙2條PWM<br />\nIR3599<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.infineon.com/dgdl/ir3599.pdf?fileId=5546d462533600a4015355cdb56a176f\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.infineon.com%2Fdgdl%2Fir3599.pdf%3FfileId%3D5546d462533600a4015355cdb56a176f&d=Dkz3eIcuz1ZryPyeMF8ZPoE4T4y%2BYV5jPOnVoTo%2FPYs%3D&h=7218bc1d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.infineon.com/dgdl/ir3599.pdf?fileId=5546d462533600a4015355cdb56a176f</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AKA3ae5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAKA3ae5.png&h=5163a477&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另一UP1911R應用<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.tomshardware.com/reviews/aorus-gtx-1080-ti-xtreme-edition,5054-2.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tomshardware.com%2Freviews%2Faorus-gtx-1080-ti-xtreme-edition%2C5054-2.html&d=Dkz3eIcuz1ZryPyeMF8ZPoE4T4y%2BYV5jPOnVoTo%2FPYs%3D&h=b43f3e2b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.tomshardware.com/reviews/aorus-gtx-1080-ti-xtreme-edition,5054-2.html</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyzCY5n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyzCY5n.jpg&h=4a8894f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPS. <br />\n連登硬件台雖然充滿ON9仔, 但唔會因為互相討論屌黎屌去就被BAM<br />\n亦唔係任何人嘅主場, 人人都可以講野, 相對地都算係已開化嘅地方<br />\n有時間做多D測試, 影清楚D重要嘅地方, 唔好車大炮, 唔好導d信得過你嘅fans買塊gaming edge配3950x"},{"pid":"f5141eeddea5abe30bcef563ca9e6c7fcb13d5e4","tid":2077544,"uid":113922,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T11:02:12.000Z","msg":"應該冇人睇得明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a55ab579c75afa269c374c80d7fc353e5ac3aec","tid":2077544,"uid":16873,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T11:06:40.000Z","msg":"技嘉賭神高汁post無人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n貪淚幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55381b0887da6b224dd1acedafff8751acd1ee0d","tid":2077544,"uid":16873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T11:07:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>技嘉賭神高汁post無人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<del>貪淚</del>幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n含淚"},{"pid":"024747d3689c95f24a57c0656acac16863a4f41f","tid":2077544,"uid":137096,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T11:28:36.000Z","msg":"666 skrskr 🤙🏿🤙🏿"},{"pid":"85ba7339793efdc11f52d1bf3d529c6d9c8cefdf","tid":2077544,"uid":259140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f5141eeddea5abe30bcef563ca9e6c7fcb13d5e4","tid":2077544,"uid":113922,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T11:02:12.000Z","msg":"應該冇人睇得明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T11:30:59.000Z","msg":"仲以為得我一個睇唔明"},{"pid":"fd7b713ef0d0287d82f020bbe14f8f0c42f2660d","tid":2077544,"uid":143284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T12:22:35.000Z","msg":"6666"},{"pid":"bb9054e20d746349a614cd52053703a56fd603a1","tid":2077544,"uid":128117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T12:59:32.000Z","msg":"又係ASROCK <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" cla